description:
So i made the new video unintentionally to long, so i'm afraid I had to separate it into two separate parts with this being part 1.

The video is about Knuckles Birthday sleepover which he invited everyone (myself included) to an awesome sleepover! It has plenty of twists and surprises in store. Stay tuned!

Also, some of you may have already noticed, but in a past video where Sonic is looking at a photo album it actually mentions knuckles birthday, and sleepover. This video is actually a prequel to that. Nice little secret I threw in huh? ;)
creator: Carl Doy
